reviewText: This is one of my most powerful treasured collections. My short opinion is try it you should like it. If you are willing to put some effort into your relationship, Michel will help get a large return on your invested (ROI) of efforts. Just do it. It's worth it.

This product was supposed to be new with an unbroken seal.  The product was not new, seal was broken and cassettes were out of order.  I am concerned as to the quality of the cassettes, but, will need to listen to them soon.
